    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "伊莉雅教会管理的某所孤儿院\\n接连发生了孩子失踪事件。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "为查明事件真相，\\n弗拉斯和皮诺赶赴现场。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "弗拉斯望着孤儿院，\\n驻足不前……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "这所孤儿院……\\n我再熟悉不过了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "诶？什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "你看资料的时候\\n并没有这么说吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "小时候的记忆已经模糊了……\\n不过现在我很确定，\\n我知道这里。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "使徒是用完就弃的工具，\\n所以大多会从孤儿里挑选候补。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "我是所谓的战争遗孤，\\n进入培养使徒候选的机构前\\n是在这里长大的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "这里是唯一可以容纳\\n不完美的我的地方。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "院长嬷嬷",
            "context": "弗拉斯！你都长这么大了啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "好久不见了。\\n院长嬷嬷……您一点都没变呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "院长嬷嬷",
            "context": "哎呀，你是想说我装嫩吗？\\n真没礼貌呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "我是说您的美丽一如往昔。\\n我们一直以您为傲。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "院长嬷嬷",
            "context": "呵呵，多谢夸奖。弗拉斯，\\n我很高兴能与你再次相见。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "院长嬷嬷",
            "context": "你都出人头地，\\n成了教会总部的教育机关干部，\\n还记得这个小地方……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "因为这所孤儿院有多好，\\n我是最清楚的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "要是其它地方也能运用这里的\\n管理方法，会有更多孤儿受益。\\n我很确信这一点。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "就容我在这里叨扰一阵子，\\n好好学习一下吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "院长嬷嬷",
            "context": "当然了，这里也是你的家，\\n你想待多久都行。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "完美的谎言啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "工作需要。\\n你发现什么可疑之处了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "目前还没有。\\n孩子们看上去也很幸福，\\n不像是有什么人失踪了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "失踪事件本身才是“完美的谎言”？\\n那怎么可能。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "走，我们去找出真相。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "几天后",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "没找到任何线索……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "待了几天后我觉得……\\n这里真是乐园一样的地方啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "幸福洋溢、充满了笑容，\\n感觉这里存在完美的爱。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "对吧……\\n和我在的时候一模一样。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "来到这里后，我想起了好多\\n一度已经遗忘的事。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "在这里我曾经每天\\n都为了得到夸奖而拼命学习，\\n为了招人喜欢而努力当个乖孩子。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "那时候，我并不完美，\\n但是有容身之处……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "真是美好的回忆呢。\\n那个……我能问一个问题吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "嗯，什么问题？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "我们试图寻找的真相\\n也许会破坏你的美好回忆。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "即便如此，\\n你也要查明真相吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "你在说什么……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "集会开始了，探查院长嬷嬷\\n私人房间的机会只有今天。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "要按计划完美行事。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "啊……是！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "（事件的真相……\\n一定会破坏弗拉斯前辈的\\n美好回忆。）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "（虽然前辈表面上看起来若无其事，\\n可如果他内心其实感到了迷惘，\\n我就要完美地……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "（我能做到吗……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "典籍、课本、日记、信件……\\n没有可疑物品呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "弗拉斯前辈？\\n你在盯着墙壁看什么？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "这房间……应该没这么小才对。\\n墙以前不在这个位置。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "诶？你确定吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "嗯。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "那么，这堵墙就是后加的。\\n墙的对面是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "有空间，很可能是密室。\\n仔细搜查！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "是！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "这里……什么也没有啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "这里……是可动的！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "墙打开了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "后辈，我们走。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "（他虽然嘴上说要完美……\\n但并不是不会伤心。）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "（弗拉斯前辈没事吗……）",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}